Package: pooledCentR
Version: 1.0-0
Encoding: UTF-8
Title: Central and marginal rejection of pooled p-values in R
Description: Compute marginal and central rejection levels and the centrality quotient for p-value pooling functions and provide the chi-squared pooled p-value to control the quotient's value, also add a Satterthwaite approximation for dependent p-values.
